63 class windTurbine
64 {
65 private:
66  std::vector<double> powerCurveWS, // windspeed: x-axis on turbine power curve
67  powerCurveKW, // power output: y-axis
68  densityCorrectedWS,
69  powerCurveRPM;
70  double cutInSpeed;
71 public:
72 
73  std::vector<double> getPowerCurveWS(){ return powerCurveWS; }
74  std::vector<double> getPowerCurveKW(){ return powerCurveKW; }
75 
76  size_t powerCurveArrayLength;
77  double rotorDiameter, hubHeight, measurementHeight, shearExponent;
78  double lossesAbsolute, lossesPercent;
79  std::string errDetails;
80 
81  windTurbine(){
82  shearExponent = -999;
83  measurementHeight = -999;
84  hubHeight = -999;
85  rotorDiameter = -999;
86  lossesAbsolute = -999;
87  lossesPercent = -999;
88  }
89  bool setPowerCurve(std::vector<double> windSpeeds, std::vector<double> powerOutput);
90 
91  double tipSpeedRatio(double windSpeed);
92 
93  bool isInitialized(){
94  if (shearExponent != -999 && measurementHeight != -999 && hubHeight != -999 && rotorDiameter != -999 && lossesAbsolute != -999 && lossesPercent != -999){
95  if (powerCurveArrayLength > 0) return true;
96  }
97  return false;
98  }
99  void turbinePower(double windVelocity, double airDensity, double *turbineOutput, double *thrustCoefficient);
100  double calculateEff(double reducedPower, double originalPower) {
101  double Eff = 0.0;
102  if (originalPower < 0.0)
103  Eff = 0.0;
104  else
105  Eff = 100.0*(reducedPower + 0.0001) / (originalPower + 0.0001);
106  return Eff;
107  }
108 };

251  eddyViscosityWakeModel(){ nTurbines = 0; }
252  eddyViscosityWakeModel(size_t numberOfTurbinesInFarm, windTurbine* wt, double turbCoeff){
253  wTurbine = wt;
254  rotorDiameter = wt->rotorDiameter;
255  if (turbCoeff >= 0 && turbCoeff <= 1) turbulenceCoeff = turbCoeff ;
256  else turbulenceCoeff = .10;
257 
258  nTurbines = numberOfTurbinesInFarm;
259  axialResolution = 0.5;
260  minThrustCoeff = 0.02;
261  nBlades = 3;
262  minDeficit = 0.0002;
263  MIN_DIAM_EV = 2;
264  EV_SCALE = 1;
265  MAX_WIND_TURBINES = 300;
266  axialResolution = 0.5; // in rotor diameters, default in openWind=0.5
267  //double radialResolution = 0.2; // in rotor diameters, default in openWind=0.2
268  double maxRotorDiameters = 50; // in rotor diameters, default in openWind=50
269  useFilterFx = true;
270  matEVWakeDeficits.resize_fill(nTurbines, (int)(maxRotorDiameters / axialResolution) + 1, 0.0); // each turbine is row, each col is wake deficit for that turbine at dist
271  matEVWakeWidths.resize_fill(nTurbines, (int)(maxRotorDiameters / axialResolution) + 1, 0.0); // each turbine is row, each col is wake deficit for that turbine at dist
272  }
